Package: eurostatRToolCustom
Title: Data Visualization and Interpretation for Short-Term Economic
        Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ludovica", "Verrieri", , "ludovica.verrieri@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0009-6343-5339"))
Description: Data visualization and interpretation for short-term economic
    analysis showing the evolution of the economic activity in the European
    Union (EU), euro area (EA) and/or Member States. The users are allowed to
    choose the time series data to be implemented (which must follow the
    specified input data format), the particular set of indicators to be
    displayed (in agreement with the input data), the visualization type (map,
    plot or table) as well as the general aspect of the tool.
